reviews.text: Decent food and service.

DO NOT WASTE YOUR $$ here. Made a mistake of trying it out and was just glad our order was just at HK$120 - but we felt it wasted. Food is tasteless, service worse than typical HK service, and again Food is bad. Avoid of you can.

First of all, we had to wait at least ten minutes with the ordering, because every waiter/waitress disappeared. Finally one of them came to our table. My girlfriend told to the waitress during the order that she wants the noodle with chicken. She even pointed to the words on the menu, so it seemed there will be no problem with this. When the noodle arrived there was no meat on it at all. We called the waitress again and told her that my girlfriend ordered the noodle with chicken. She took the plate away for fifteen minutes. She turned up again with the plate and basically threw the plate on the table with the "Chicken, okay?" question and a memorable expression on her face. On top of that the food was flavourless and for sure not what you'd expect for ~70 HKD. Finally we got the bill with an overcharge of 15 HKD. I assume this was the tip for the perfect service. Or the price of the topping.
Lousy service unless you are a HK local. If you're foreigner they will be racist against you. Eat something else, like the watami downstairs 😏 better service there
Lousy service staff miss our ordee and insist they are right

reviews.text: 尖沙咀の繁華街にありながら、ビルの3階ということもあり、いつもそんなにひどく混雑することもなく、ゆっくりできる。料理はステーキなど西洋のものより、例えば海南鶏飯とかサテーなどの中華系、マレー系？シンガポール系？のものをオーダーした方が日本人の味覚には合うように思う。

下午茶喺尖沙咀中算平同抵食
大部分下午茶餐連加一都係40蚊
好多附近返工既人都黎幫襯
食物普通 坐得都算舒適 有時人比較多
侍應服務麻麻地
價錢質素滿意
Decent food and service.
食物Ok

Normal Priced Meals
